    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pointed arches located at the culmination of a wall in Russian church architecture. They differ from "zakomaras" in having a a purely decorative rather than a structural purpose.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
